I had this problem too and found out that it is a problem with the saved directory.

It should be in something like C:/program files/Electronic Arts/Spore/Spore

I know I already said that about the .DLLs but this happened to me and it has to be in the Spore folder within the other Spore folder.
I have also had a copy of Galactic Adventures that said that and it was a copy of the Galactic Adventures extension, not the install. So make sure your copy is good.

